# 🏗️ Implementation Plan — Academic Integrity Analyzer (PS2)

> **Goal**: Build a complete Academic Integrity Analyzer in 24 hours, committing feature-by-feature, with 80% correctness + 20% completeness scoring.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack — Final Decision

| Layer | Technology | Why This Over Alternatives |
|-------|-----------|---------------------------|
| **Backend** | **Python 3.12 + FastAPI** | Team already knows FastAPI from Nova. Async support. Best PDF/NLP ecosystem. Auto-generated API docs at `/docs`. |
| **Frontend** | **Vanilla HTML + CSS + JS** | Zero build step = zero config bugs. Instant deploy. No React/TS compilation issues eating hackathon time. Serves from any static host. |
| **PDF Parsing** | **pdfplumber** | Superior to PyPDF2 for layout-aware text extraction. Handles columns, tables, headers. |
| **AI — Style Analysis** | **OpenAI GPT-4o-mini** | Fast, cheap ($0.15/1M input tokens). Perfect for per-paragraph bulk analysis. |
| **AI — Report Gen** | **OpenAI GPT-4o** | Smarter model for final synthesis and forensic reasoning. |
| **AI — Embeddings** | **text-embedding-3-small** | Cheapest embedding model. 1536 dimensions. For semantic source matching. |
| **NLP Helpers** | **NLTK** | Sentence tokenization, word tokenization. Lighter than spaCy (no model download). |
| **Source Search** | **arxiv Python package** | Free API, no auth needed, returns paper metadata + abstracts. |
| **Visualization** | **Chart.js** (CDN) | Heatmaps, line charts, bar charts. Zero npm install — just a script tag. |
| **Deployment** | **Render (backend) + Vercel (frontend)** | Free tier, GitHub auto-deploy, SSL included. |
| **Version Control** | **GitHub** | Required by rules. Fresh repo at hackathon start. |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> ### Why NOT React/Vite?
> In a 24hr hackathon, every minute spent on `npm install`, TS errors, build failures, and Vite config is a minute NOT spent on features. Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS means:
> - `index.html` opens instantly in any browser
> - No build step = no build bugs
> - Deploy by dragging folder to Vercel
> - Frontend person (M3) can start immediately without any setup

