**What to handle**:
- Empty PDF → clear error message
- Image-only/scanned PDF → "No text detected" error
- Very short paper (1–2 paragraphs) → "Insufficient content" warning
- Very long paper (100+ paragraphs) → truncate to first 50 with notice
- Paper with no references → skip citation analysis, note in report
- Non-English text → warning message
- API timeout/failure → retry logic + partial results
- Invalid file type → reject with message
- Large file (>10MB) → reject with size limit error

